---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const title = 'Support — Docket for iOS';
const description = 'Get help with the Docket iOS app. FAQ, quick add syntax, and contact information.';
---

<Base title={title} description={description}>
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <img src="/logo-mark.svg" alt="Docket" width="28" height="28" />
        Docket
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/#app">iOS App</a>
        <a href="/#emacs">Emacs</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/jonathanchu/docket" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="page">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="label">Docket for iOS</span>
      <h1>Support</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Need help? You're in the right place.</p>

      <section class="content">
        <h2>Get Help</h2>
        <p>If you're having trouble with Docket, please open an issue on GitHub:</p>
        <p><a href="https://github.com/jonathanchu/docket-app/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/jonathanchu/docket-app/issues</a></p>
        <p>You can also email <a href="mailto:hello@docketgtd.com">hello@docketgtd.com</a>.</p>

        <h2>How do I set up Dropbox sync?</h2>
        <p>During onboarding, select "Dropbox" and sign in to your Dropbox account. Then choose the org file you want to sync. The default path is <code>/org/gtd.org</code>.</p>

        <h2>Can I use Docket without sync?</h2>
        <p>Yes. Choose "Local Only" during setup. Docket will use a bundled example file so you can try it out, or you can create tasks from scratch. You can connect a sync provider later in Settings.</p>

        <h2>Will Docket change my org file formatting?</h2>
        <p>No. Docket preserves every line of your org file exactly as-is. Only the specific lines affected by your edits are modified. Your Emacs setup stays untouched.</p>

        <h2>What org-mode features are supported?</h2>
        <p>Docket supports TODO states (TODO, NEXT, WAIT, SOMEDAY, DONE, CANCELLED), priorities ([#A], [#B], [#C]), tags, SCHEDULED, DEADLINE, and CLOSED timestamps. Level-1 headings are treated as projects, level-2 headings as tasks.</p>

        <h2>Quick Add syntax</h2>
        <p>Use natural language shortcuts when adding tasks:</p>
        <div class="syntax-table">
          <div class="syntax-row">
            <code>#tag</code>
            <span>Add a tag</span>
          </div>
          <div class="syntax-row">
            <code>p1</code> / <code>p2</code> / <code>p3</code>
            <span>Set priority (A, B, C)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="syntax-row">
            <code>today</code> / <code>tomorrow</code> / <code>monday</code>
            <span>Schedule a date</span>
          </div>
          <div class="syntax-row">
            <code>+3d</code>
            <span>Schedule N days from now</span>
          </div>
          <div class="syntax-row">
            <code>!deadline</code>
            <span>Make the date a deadline</span>
          </div>
          <div class="syntax-row">
            <code>/Project</code>
            <span>File under a project</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-left">
        <span class="footer-logo">Docket</span>
        <span class="footer-muted">GTD productivity tools</span>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/jonathanchu/docket" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
        <a href="mailto:hello@docketgtd.com">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Base>

<style>
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(13, 13, 20, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .nav-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .logo:hover { color: var(--color-text); }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .nav-links a { color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--color-text); }

  .page {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--color-ios);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: block;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .content h2 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .content code {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .syntax-table {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .syntax-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .syntax-row span {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .footer-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-left {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .footer-logo { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; }
  .footer-muted { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }

  .footer-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .footer-links a { color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--color-text); }
</style>
